fields.name: Destination
fields.description: Life is so busy now that we all need time to switch off. Whether that means sitting by a pool or dancing the night away; you need to leave your worries behind you, let off some steam and have a good time on holiday.

fields.name: Hotel
fields.description: What's your favorite thing when staying at a nice hotel? Amenities, comfortable beds, big bathrooms and showers/ tubs and more.

fields.name: Tour
fields.description: You get to see a place, its culture, treasures, and big sites, taste the cuisine, blend with the locals and then you're off again.

fields.name: Peru, Lima
fields.description: Located in the coast of the Pacific Ocean, Lima is the capital of Peru, and it is a city of surprises and contrasts. It is the result of a marvelous fusion of different cultures: European and Andean traditions are merged together in their streets, museums, monuments and people

fields.name: Hotel Edison Times Square
fields.description: Ideally located in Times Square, this Manhattan hotel has been around since 1930. right in the heart of the theatre district

fields.name: Park Plaza Westminster Bridge London Hotel
fields.description: Located on the South Bank of the Thames, Park Plaza Westminster Bridge London is set opposite the Houses of Parliament and Big Ben.

fields.name: Germany, Berlin
fields.description: Berlin is the ideal place for a city break in Europe. Ticking all the boxes, the buzzing metropolis boasts a killer nightlife scene, amazing local food, a rich history, world famous beer and some of the most remarkable sights and museums in the world.

fields.name: London Tower Bridge Tour
fields.description: Tower Bridge is a Grade I listed combined bascule and suspension bridge in London, built between 1886 and 1894, designed by Horace Jones and engineered by John Wolfe Barry with the help of Henry Marc

fields.name: Royalton New York
fields.description: This New York City hotel is located on 44th Street and is 322 metres from Times Square. It features on-site dining and guest rooms with flat-screen TVs.

fields.name: Millennium Gloucester Hotel London
fields.description: Situated in stylish Kensington, the 4-star Millennium Gloucester Hotel London is 100 metres from Gloucester Road Tube Station.

fields.name: The Aoyama Grand Hotel, Tokyo
fields.description: Set in Tokyo, 300 metres from The Watarium Museum of Contemporary Art, THE AOYAMA GRAND HOTEL offers accommodation with a restaurant, private parking and a bar.
